<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826CB8FE58FEE5FE6B" bold="true" box="[189,259,466,492]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Notes</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7C0636AC7453FF826CB8FD8BFEB1FD68" blockId="16.[187,1400,513,751]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<bibRefCitation id="18284B5D7453FF826CB8FD8BFE62FD9B" author="Bradley J. C." box="[189,388,513,540]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 38" refId="ref32187" refString="Bradley J. C. 1964 b. The Fabrician types of Scoliidae (Hymenoptera), with notes and an appendix by J. G. Betrem. Spolia Zoologica Musei Hauniensis 21: 1 - 38." type="journal article" year="1964">Bradley (1964b)</bibRefCitation>
listed the name “ 
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826E68FD8BFCEAFD9C" box="[621,780,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Phaleromeris</emphasis>
” as a subgenus for 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826811FD8BFACAFD9C" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1793" box="[1044,1324,513,539]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Campsomeris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulata">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826811FD8BFACAFD9C" box="[1044,1324,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Campsomeris annulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(now 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826CB8FDAEFE0AFDB9" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1793" box="[189,492,548,574]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Campsomeriella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulata">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826CB8FDAEFE0AFDB9" box="[189,492,548,574]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Campsomeriella annulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). No description was provided, making the name a nomen nudum, and Bradley noted that one would appear in a forthcoming paper by Betrem. Subsequently, Betrem (in 
<bibRefCitation id="18284B5D7453FF8268F2FDCDFEBCFD02" author="Bradley J. C. &amp; Betrem J. G." pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="287 - 327" refId="ref32226" refString="Bradley J. C. &amp; Betrem J. G. 1967. The types of the Scoliidae described by Frederick Smith (Hymenoptera) with descriptions of new taxa, and notes on the Oriental localities where Alfred Russel Wallace collected. Bulletin of the British Museum (Natural History). Entomology 20 (7): 287 - 327." type="journal article" year="1967">Bradley &amp; Betrem 1967</bibRefCitation>
) described the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826E8DFDE0FCC7FD03" authorityName="Betrem" authorityYear="1967" box="[648,801,618,644]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Phalerimeris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826E8DFDE0FCC7FD03" box="[648,801,618,644]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Phalerimeris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826F63FDE0FB14FD02" authority="de Saussure, 1858" authorityName="de Saussure" authorityYear="1858" box="[870,1266,618,645]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Elis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phalerata">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826F63FDE0FBE9FD03" box="[870,1039,618,644]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Elis phalerata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="18284B5D7453FF82681FFDE0FB14FD02" author="de Saussure H. L. F." box="[1050,1266,618,645]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="193 - 249" refId="ref34335" refString="de Saussure H. L. F. 1858. Description de diverses especes nouvelles ou peu connues du genre Scolia. Annales de la Societe entomologique de France, troisieme serie 6: 193 - 249." type="journal article" year="1858">de Saussure, 1858</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
designated as 
<typeStatus id="A302880E7453FF826CDAFD04FEF4FD2F" box="[223,274,654,680]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">type</typeStatus>
species. 
<bibRefCitation id="18284B5D7453FF826D7FFD04FDDAFD2F" author="Argaman Q." box="[378,572,653,680]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="171 - 222" refId="ref31690" refString="Argaman Q. 1996. Generic synopsis of Scoliidae (Hymenoptera, Scolioidea). Annales Historico- Naturales Musei Nationalis Hungarici 88: 171 - 222." type="journal article" year="1996">Argaman (1996)</bibRefCitation>
incorrectly regarded 
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826F32FD04FC30FD2F" box="[823,982,654,680]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Phaleromeris</emphasis>
as available from 
<bibRefCitation id="18284B5D7453FF8268ABFD04FA94FD2F" author="Bradley J. C." box="[1198,1394,653,680]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 38" refId="ref32187" refString="Bradley J. C. 1964 b. The Fabrician types of Scoliidae (Hymenoptera), with notes and an appendix by J. G. Betrem. Spolia Zoologica Musei Hauniensis 21: 1 - 38." type="journal article" year="1964">Bradley (1964b)</bibRefCitation>
, with 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826CF2FD3BFE76FD4C" authorityName="Betrem" authorityYear="1967" box="[247,400,689,715]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Phalerimeris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826CF2FD3BFE76FD4C" box="[247,400,689,715]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Phalerimeris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a subsequent spelling variation, and proposed the unnecessary name 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF8268D6FD3BFAABFD4C" authorityName="Argaman" authorityYear="1996" box="[1235,1357,689,715]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Batalanga" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF8268D6FD3BFAABFD4C" box="[1235,1357,689,715]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Batalanga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for 
<taxonomicName id="BBB94D2F7453FF826CB8FD5FFEB6FD69" authorityName="de Saussure" authorityYear="1858" box="[189,336,724,750]" class="Insecta" family="Scoliidae" genus="Elis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phalerata">
<emphasis id="4ECDEABE7453FF826CB8FD5FFEB6FD69" box="[189,336,724,750]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">E. phalerata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
